collectionMetadata.name: Volume of Mail Handled by Type, Annual
collectionMetadata.description:
The postal statistics published on IDA website prior to Jun 09 refer to statistics for SingPost only. The postal statistics published for Jun 09 and after comprise the aggregated statistics of all postal services operators in Singapore.

Mail volume includes ordinary and registered mail.

The decline in stamp vendors was largely attributed to the exit of a convenience store group as stamp vendors.
